Union Token has eof; integer value: i64; operator symbol: u8 and precedence: u8.

To make operator, giving Token.
Give Token.operator with symbol be 10 and precedence be 5.

To main, giving i32.
Let token be make operator.
Give match token:
Token.operator with symbol and precedence gives (symbol as i32) plus (precedence as i32);
otherwise gives 0.
